{"tid":1728776,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【法律撚請入】基本法第十八條=出動老解無違反憲法？","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T10:54:02.000Z","uid":311279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa0690b4417b67d88875faab4460a6cf5e229e1","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小妹喺ig開左個小小嘅文宣page<br />\n(@walleyfei 求follow)<br />\n咁今日就叫大家煲大老解自發執垃圾係違反憲法咁啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點知釣到隻高學歷五毛出黎同我講法律<br />\n一直強調第18條 內容如下</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaVOBYC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaVOBYC.png&h=ccda293b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/essentials-1516ise07-applying-national-laws-in-hong-kong.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fresearch-publications%2Fchinese%2Fessentials-1516ise07-applying-national-laws-in-hong-kong.htm&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=6f868f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/essentials-1516ise07-applying-national-laws-in-hong-kong.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n咁我就做左少少資料搜集<br />\n本人生性愚笨但係以下係我嘅解讀<br />\n<br />\n只有 一 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">徵詢其所屬的香港特別行政區基本法委員會<br />\n和香港特別行政區政府的同意後 </span></strong><br />\nor<br />\n二 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>全國人大常委會決定宣布戰爭狀態</strong></span><br />\nor<br />\n三 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港內發生香港政府不能控制的危及國家統一或安全的動亂而決定香港進入緊急狀態</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢三種情況下 中央人民政府先可以發布命令將有關全國性法律在香港實施</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁逐個反駁啦<br />\n一就一定無啦 臨奠尋日大條斯理割席<br />\n二同三我唔清楚<br />\n不過呢類全國性法律係要以原文照錄方式實施 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐係就算甴大大真係宣布香港進入緊急/戰爭狀態<br />\n呢條例都要由行政長官公布或藉本地立法先可以實施</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n啲五毛成日想用呢條黎作為論點 合理化老解擅自出黎執垃圾<br />\n但係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨奠公布左咩？本地立咗法咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知解讀得岩唔岩 智商有限<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求救識法律嘅手足 救救文宣組 唔想比人騎住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f65f8391eaf742e9611b4200afede037fc30623","tid":1728776,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先73%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=098f1c42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=479bc9d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"98f9326d03650987df96429c8c8becb7dcbad7f9","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"7a1e165e35eff00b3764321a978ffe4d04f1981a","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"a7db3405dfd47b948be28840763b7ffaca5322a6","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"565e069452ca79d854ff0f8240f70a692f4389f2","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"f9e14a9a40c1ddd149c743412f895055b9b532f0","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"b206df669d0b35500470bf0efb99682f15d49e38","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"4b050d1fa622ac81ace7b6f23ae35aecb6ca03f0","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"0fd9d67ab79df71b19dd0087534a1bc46229dfb9","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"d866b62a41f0c42089672a94592ba17cf1815351","tid":1728776,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pi